                  "display": "Summarization of encounter note"
                }
              ]
            },
            "title": "Synthesis"
          },
          {
            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Dear colleague, we are writing to inform you regarding your patient, a 56-year-old male admitted for pre-renal transplant evaluation. During his stay from 29th to 31st December 2008, a comprehensive transplant workup was completed. This included renal function assessment, cardiovascular evaluation, serological and infectious disease screening, immunological typing and cross-matching, as well as urological and general surgical fitness assessment. Imaging studies including renal ultrasound and chest X-ray were performed. The patient demonstrated acceptable surgical and medical fitness for transplantation. All required preparatory steps have been fulfilled and the patient has been formally listed on the kidney transplant waiting list. Dialysis preparatory care planning has been initiated as per protocol (ICD-10: Z49.0). We recommend continued close monitoring of renal function and cardiovascular status in your practice pending transplant availability. Please do not hesitate to contact us with any queries.</div>"
            },
